    "The PIL is carefully designed to evaluate the likelihood of information accuracy, employing advanced statistical models to systematically assess and enhance the fidelity of the data retrieved.",
    "This approach not only aims to refine the accuracy of information retrieval but also to elevate the overall reliability and trustworthiness of the output generated by the Mistral model.",
    "By leveraging this innovative layer, this study aspires to make a substantive contribution to the field, establishing probabilistic inference as a pivotal element in the evolution and maturation of LLMs, particularly in their application for reliable and precise information retrieval across diverse domains.Below is a list of the major contributions of this study:1.",
    "Introduction of a Probabilistic Inference Layer (PIL) into the Mistral Large Language Model, fundamentally enhancing its information retrieval accuracy and reliability. 2.",
